    "We find the best β stays relatively consistent across different dataset sizes.",
    "Tuning Beta Beta β is a hyperparameter in DPO that controls the strength of KL-divergence.",
    "Besides sequence length and reference model, many prior work (Tunstall et al., 2023b; Gorbatovski et al., 2024) also differs in the choice of β.",
